Description:
Moving next to the big pit in the middle of the room you come to a ledge.

Clearly, those cultists are throwing something in there ... but you're not sure what it could be.

The hole looks really deep and you can't see the bottom, plus there is no apparent way down.
DescriptionAction: Do you want to try throwing something?
